<font color="#FF0000">SS MAYAGUEZ</font><br>
<tt>Fri Dec 27 16:54:59 US/Eastern 1996
</tt><p>
In response to the the people looking for information and discussing the S.S. Mayaguez.  Did you read the good article in May 1996 Soldier of Fortune.  It discribed the MIA recovery efforts and also the story of the battle.  In regards to the three missing men, the article claims they were a M-60 machine-gun fire team that covered the withdrawal and were left behind in the process.  One of these men was possibly executed by the enemy after the battle.  Check out the article, it was pretty informative.  Thought this info might help the person requesting info on the Mayaguez.  
<p><code>--   (Joe) </code><p>


